25
00:03:30,322 --> 00:03:32,922
<font color="#ffff00">How can we not leave a trace
while we're alive?</font>

26
00:03:34,922 --> 00:03:36,362
<font color="#ffff00">Don't talk back to me.</font>

27
00:03:37,082 --> 00:03:40,282
<font color="#ffff00">The sign of life you're referring to
